1 SECTION 6.3. If any section or provision of this act is declared unconstitutional or
2 invalid by the courts, it does not affect the validity of this act as a whole or any part other than
3 the part so declared to be unconstitutional or invalid.
4
5 EFFECTIVE DATE
6 SECTION 6.4. Except as otherwise provided, this act is effective when it becomes
7 law.
